title: Kalicharan
subTitle: When Prabhakar, an honest cop, is murdered by Din Dayal, a powerful crime lord, Khanna recruits his doppelganger Kalicharan to defeat Din Dayal.

title: Naach Uthe Sansaar
subTitle: A rich man's daughter falls in love with a farmer and wants to marry him. However, her father not only disapproves of this but also humiliates his mother, which makes the farmer seek vengeance.

title: Pyar Kiye Jaa
subTitle: Ramlal, a widower, struggles to find suitable grooms for his daughters and to control his son's film obsession. To make matters worse, one of his former employees launches a protest against him.

title: My Life My Story
subTitle: The host invites prominent Bollywood celebrities who open up about their personal life and share interesting anecdotes based on their experiences.

title: Jawani Diwani
subTitle: Vijay meets Neeta, the daughter of a Thakur, and falls in love with her. However, things change after he finds out that she has been promised to another man in marriage.

title: Saas Bhi Kabhi Bahu Thi
subTitle: When Sadhana marries Deepak, her manipulative mother urges her to harass her mother-in-law. Subsequently, she also meddles in her son's marriage, turning their lives into a web of misery.

title: Sangam
subTitle: Two best friends, Sundar and Gopal, love the same woman, Radha, while she has feelings only for Gopal. But when Sundar marries Radha, the love triangle is thrown into turmoil.

title: Aakhree Raasta
subTitle: A man is falsely accused of his wife's murder and imprisoned. When he sets out to seek revenge, he finds a police officer on his trail who turns out to be his own son.

title: Mard
subTitle: Azad, a wealthy prosperous king, is locked in a dungeon by General Dyer who wants to take over his kingdom. Years later, Azad's son comes to his father's rescue and puts an end to Dyer's tyranny.

title: Yeh Vaada Raha
subTitle: Vikram, in love with Sunita, faces tragedy when an accident leaves him unaware of her transformation, while Sunita, now under a new identity secretly hopes to rekindle their love.

title: Yeh Vaada Raha
subTitle: Vikram, in love with Sunita, faces tragedy when an accident leaves him unaware of her transformation, while Sunita, now under a new identity secretly hopes to rekindle their love.

title: Awaara
subTitle: Born into poverty, Raj steals and works for a criminal gang in order to feed his mother. But when he meets and falls in love with his childhood friend, Rita, he vows to change his ways.

title: Biwi O Biwi
subTitle: To overcome with his love for Asha, singer Chandermohan masquerades as an army officer when her father, a retired military officer, refuses to let her marry a civilian.

title: Dastaan-E-Rafi
subTitle: Renowned celebrities discuss the life journey of gifted singer Mohammed Rafi, sharing moments and incidents they experienced with him during his career.

title: Piya Ka Ghar
subTitle: Malti falls in love with Ram and marries him without knowing what to expect. When she goes to his house, she realises that he is very poor and she is stuck with him for the rest of her life.

title: Pataal Bhairavi
subTitle: Ramu, a poor man, falls for a princess, but her father forbids the relation due to Ramu's poverty. Later, things take a turn for the worse when Ramu becomes rich, but it endangers his paramour.

title: Padosan
subTitle: Bhola enlists the help of his musician friends to woo the girl next door, Bindu, by making her think he is a great singer. But when the ruse is eventually discovered, it threatens their relationship.

title: Insaaf Ki Pukar
subTitle: When a dishonest officer destroys their lives, two men unite to fight corruption, facing danger as they strive to restore honour and peace.

title: Rajput
subTitle: Janaki, a young woman, loves Manu Pratap Singh but is forced to marry Dhirendra, a police inspector. However, when she gets kidnapped by a man, who tries to rape her, Manu saves her in time.

title: Karz
subTitle: Monty discovers the shocking truth about his past life when he was killed by his gold-digger wife, while his family was rendered homeless. Supported by his lover, he decides to set things right.

title: Karz
subTitle: Monty discovers the shocking truth about his past life when he was killed by his gold-digger wife, while his family was rendered homeless. Supported by his lover, he decides to set things right.

title: Zehreela Insaan
subTitle: Arjun, a short-tempered person, falls in love with Margaret, but her family is against their relationship. The couple elopes, but destiny forces the duo to commit suicide.

title: Priyatama
subTitle: Despite having made the difficult decision to separate, Dolly pretends to love her husband when her father comes to visit.

title: Aap Ke Deewane
subTitle: Forced to become college dropouts, childhood friends Ram and Rahim put on quirky disguises to get hired as home tutors for a wealthy and sheltered woman. As they spend time with her, a love triangle starts taking shape.

title: Gopal Krishna
subTitle: King Kansa claims the throne of Mathura and kills off his nephews to prevent his death at one of their hands. However, the eighth child is whisked off to safety and grows up as Krishna.

title: Saudagar
subTitle: Moti betrays his loyal wife and business partner, Majubee, to marry his true love, Phoolbanu. However, his selfish act unleashes unforeseen consequences that upend his life.

title: Meri Aawaz Suno
subTitle: Sushil Kumar, a police officer, is charged with the task of apprehending a gang of kidnappers, who only target women. However, doing so not only threatens his identity and life but also his family's.

title: Amardeep
subTitle: Raja, an arrogant man, is in love with his servant's daughter, Radha. He is enraged to find that she loves Kishan, so he hatches a devious plan to get them married and then keep them apart.

title: Andheri Raat Mein Diya Tere Haath Mein
subTitle: Two friends join the underworld to make money and to lead a comfortable life. Later, they realise the ill-effects of crime and want to lead a normal life.
